data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-sided brick residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, providing the perfect blend of elegance and comfort. Nestled on a spacious .40-acre lot, this property offers a sense of tranquility and privacy. The fully fenced yard ensures security, making it an ideal haven for families and pets alike. With double garage doors and a sunroom, this home seamlessly combines functionality with luxury. Enjoy the seamless flow of the sunlit interiors, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home – schedule a showing today and experience the charm for yourself!
